0.9.1
-----
- Meson build system
- Added DFBTERM_NO_SCROLLBAR environment variable

0.8.15 (February 2 2007)
------
- Allow to paste using the right mouse button
- Follow LiTE API changes
- Scroll line-by-line when Shift key is pressed

0.8.0 (February 28 2005)
-----
- Add scrolling via mouse wheel, scroll indicator is two lines thick
- Added selection using mouse and copy-and-paste support
- Set content and opacity blend mode to auto
- Set default size to 100x30
- Maintain a flipping region that is flushed after all updates are done
- Use Misc-Fixed font

0.0.0 (October 23 2002)
-----
- Original code by Denis Oliver Kropp
